# Apps Directory

Each application lives in its own subdirectory with its own configuration.

Structure for each app:
```
src/apps/your-app/
├── App.tsx
├── main.tsx
├── index.css
├── index.html
├── vite.config.ts
├── tsconfig.json
├── components/
└── public/
```

Apps can import from shared libs using the @/ alias:
```typescript
import { formatCount } from '@/libs/utils/format';
```

Add dev/build scripts to root package.json:
```json
"scripts": {
  "dev:your-app": "cd src/apps/your-app && vite",
  "build:your-app": "cd src/apps/your-app && tsc --noEmit && vite build"
}
```
